    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whispers Of The Shadow 是一款故事驱动的第一人称生存恐怖游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在收到关于侦探格雷斯·劳森失踪的继妹艾米的线索后，两名警察迅速前往指定的地点。当格蕾丝得知消息时，她立即出发，抵达现场后，遇到了一个可怕的场景：她的警察同事的尸体。就在她试图理解发生了什么时，她突然发现自己被困在屋内。现在，格蕾丝只有一个目标：找到失踪的妹妹并逃离这个噩梦。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whispers Of The Shadow 的核心游戏机制之一是寻找和使用蜡烛。蜡烛是一个关键资源，不仅能照亮阴影，还能作为抵御敌人的屏障。为了照亮周围环境并保护自己不受敌人伤害，你必须在黑暗中前进，策略性地放置和点燃蜡烛，以免迷失方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/aa8ef4fa1b8916f75fea3be0979402cc.poster.avif?t=1771923033\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/aa8ef4fa1b8916f75fea3be0979402cc.webm?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/aa8ef4fa1b8916f75fea3be0979402cc.mp4?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/7bfcfc8784f13bd6157da29523a49d11.poster.avif?t=1771923033\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/7bfcfc8784f13bd6157da29523a49d11.webm?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/7bfcfc8784f13bd6157da29523a49d11.mp4?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你使用的是手动发电手电筒，而不是传统手电筒。由于在为手电筒充电时发出的声音，如果敌人靠近，它会导致敌人听到你的动静并追赶你。因此，你需要节省手电筒电池的能量，仔细使用和充电。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/baf1cef82bf71cd179ab5739707973c7.poster.avif?t=1771923033\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/baf1cef82bf71cd179ab5739707973c7.webm?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084700/extras/baf1cef82bf71cd179ab5739707973c7.mp4?t=1771923033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
